{"tid":480990,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺D貓撚好嘔心","createTime":"2017-11-26T16:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T08:24:47.000Z","uid":17932,"like":136,"dislike":165,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"2a646166c1ec5345eabdecf8ff122f3e37753eea","tid":480990,"uid":17932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:40:16.000Z","msg":"頂唔撚順出面幾十個POST都係影自己養個隻畜牲出黎<br />\n又吹捧自己隻貓幾咁可愛<br />\n俾隻畜牲整到又話百厭係咁<br />\n影到個D畜牲樣樣衰衰都有D貓撚話好正<br />\n咁低質既垃圾POST都可以有正評<br />\n平時D港男出去已經要受氣,慘D既仲俾班臭雞收兵做狗<br />\n番到去屋企仲要自稱貓奴,叫隻畜牲做主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗都識擔下報紙拖鞋啦<br />\n貓就乜撚都唔識,扮個閪樣出黎,D貓撚又話佢地高傲乜乜77<br />\n淨係講養貓都睇得出班港男幾撚廢,抵佢地一世俾港女食住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38f7347c93eaf8fe838cb400cc7abf8a6291830","tid":480990,"uid":113178,"like":46,"dislike":3,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T17:04:38.000Z","msg":"連登仔貓都要反 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d90a7384f180ecc981ec263dfe8648c1cd257d","tid":480990,"uid":36849,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cd1aee7b8a5b701fe5871e1c9223ee498584376","tid":480990,"uid":17932,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T17:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫d動物整對白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係十足十弱智仔"},{"pid":"7e28475c9d2c9d7f9b1e2725a5c4c8efdac943b9","tid":480990,"uid":79786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T17:30:26.000Z","msg":"不嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\